    "Name": "Hermes II",
    "Details": "The primary weapon on the -2S is an AC/5 in the right torso, with a single ton of ammo in the left torso. The 'Mech carries limited secondary weapons, only a medium laser in the right arm as well as a flamer in the left. The rest of the stats of the 'Mech are pretty normal for its size and time of design, 7.5 tons of standard armor, a 240-rated engine core and 10 single heat sinks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.02</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
